'''維斯托·梅爾文·斯里弗'''（{{lang-en|'''Vesto Melvin Slipher'''}}，{{bd|1875年|11月11日|1969年|11月8日|catIdx=S}}）<ref name="nytimes1969">{{Citation| publication-date = November 10, 1969| date = November 9, 1969| title = Nesto (sic) Slipher, 93, Astronomer, Dies| periodical = [[紐約時報|The New York Times]]| place = Flagstaff, AZ| page = 47| issn = 1452424| accessdate = 2008-04-17}}</ref>，美國天文學家。其弟[[厄爾·查爾斯·斯里弗|厄爾·查爾斯·斯里弗]]也是天文學家，並且是羅威爾天文台台長。

== 生平 ==
斯里弗生於美國印第安那州[[茂比利_(印第安那州)|茂比利]]，並在1909年於[[印第安纳大学布卢明顿分校|印第安纳大学布卢明顿分校]]完成學業<ref name="nytimes1969"/>。他畢生職業生涯都在亞利桑那州[[弗拉格斯塔夫_(亚利桑那州)|旗桿市]]的[[羅威爾天文台|羅威爾天文台]]度過，於1915年擔任副台長、1916年擔任代理台長，1926年擔任台長直到1952年退休<ref name="nytimes1969"/>。他使用[[光譜|光譜]]判定行星的自轉周期和大氣層的成分。1912年他首次在星系的譜線中發現了[[紅移|紅移]]<ref>Slipher first reports on the making the first Doppler measurement on September 17, 1912 in [http://adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-bib_query?bibcode=1913LowOB...1b..56S&db_key=AST&data_type=HTML&format=&high=448f04e38822894 ''The radial velocity of the Andromeda Nebula''] {{Wayback|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-bib_query?bibcode=1913LowOB...1b..56S&db_key=AST&data_type=HTML&format=&high=448f04e38822894 |date=20200728181811 }} in the inaugural volume of the ''Lowell Observatory Bulletin'', pp.2.56-2.57. In his report Slipher writes: "The magnitude of this velocity, which is the greatest hitherto observed, raises the question whether the velocity-like displacement might not be due to some other cause, but I believe we have at present no other interpretation for it." Three years later, Slipher wrote a review in the journal ''Popular Astronomy'', Vol. 23, p. 21-24 [http://adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-bib_query?bibcode=1915PA.....23...21S&db_key=AST&data_type=HTML&format=&high=448f04e38822894 ''Spectrographic Observations of Nebulae''] {{Wayback|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-bib_query?bibcode=1915PA.....23...21S&db_key=AST&data_type=HTML&format=&high=448f04e38822894 |date=20200728181833 }}, in which he states, "The early discovery that the great Andromeda spiral had the quite exceptional velocity of - 300 km(/s) showed the means then available, capable of investigating not only the spectra of the spirals but their velocities as well." Slipher reported the velocities for 15 spiral nebula spread across the entire [[天球|celestial sphere]], all but three having observable "positive" (that is recessional) velocities.</ref>。1929年在地球大氣層的[[中氣層|中氣層]]中發現了[[鈉層|鈉層]] <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.albany.edu/faculty/rgk/atm101/sodium.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-09-01 |archive-date=2017-07-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731164638/http://www.albany.edu/faculty/rgk/atm101/sodium.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他也僱用了[[克莱德·汤博|克莱德·汤博]]並支持其工作，促使他在1930年發現了[[冥王星|冥王星]]<ref name="nytimes1969" />。

[[愛德文·哈勃|愛德文·哈勃]]常被錯誤認為是[[星系|星系]][[紅移|紅移]]的發現者<ref>This had actually been observed by Vesto Slipher in the 1910s, but the world was largely unaware. Ref: Slipher (1917): Proc. Amer. Phil. Soc., 56, 403.</ref>。紅移的量測和確認是由{{link-en|詹姆士·愛德華·凱勒|James Edward Keeler}}（任職於[[利克天文台|利克天文台]]和[[阿利根尼天文台|阿利根尼天文台]]）、維斯托·斯里弗（羅威爾天文台）和[[威廉·華萊士·坎貝爾|威廉·華萊士·坎貝爾]]（[[利克天文台|利克天文台]]）等人完成。 

哈伯和他的助手[[米爾頓·赫馬森|米爾頓·赫馬森]]（Milton Humason）結合了自有的星系距離量測資料和斯里弗的星系紅移資料，發現了星系的距離和紅移的粗略關係式。紅移和距離的關係式於1929年由哈伯和赫馬森提出，今天稱為[[哈伯定律|哈伯定律]]，並且是現代[[空间的度规膨胀|宇宙膨脹]]模型的基礎。

斯里弗在[[弗拉格斯塔夫_(亚利桑那州)|旗桿市]]去世並葬於當地公墓<ref name="nytimes1969"/>。

